metadata.name: Bunnyland Valentines Collection #2
metadata.description:
Our Valentines Collection is the most adorable NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain inspired by two real inseparable rabbits called Chiko and Moshu in Sydney Australia.  Stored as ERC721 tokens in 1000x1000 resolution, this collection consists of 5,000 unique and randomly generated NFTs. Each NFT is generated from 50+ traits.  These traits and symbols portray the celebration of love, romance, respect and friendship.   
A community-driven project, the holders of the token can participate in exclusive events such as NFT games, raffles, community giveaways and educational Webinars.
